  "stem": "<p>Which expression is equivalent to (<i>b</i> + 7)/(<i>a</i> &minus; 5) + <i>b</i>(<i>a</i> &minus; 5)/(<i>a</i>&sup2;<i>b</i> &minus; 5<i>ab</i>)?</p>",
